For Building Owners:
•	Account registration and login using NID.
•	Registering buildings and flats with accurate location details.
•	Adding, updating, and deleting tenant and domestic worker information.
•	Assigning tenants and workers to specific flats.
•	Viewing complete details of registered buildings, flats, tenants, and workers through a dashboard.
•	Accessing a “Show All Info” table with search and filter functionalities.
•	Managing personal profile information (view and edit).
•	Password recovery through OTP/code verification.
•	Secure logout functionality
